{"tid":1787034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府第二場社區對話結束 商經局局長邱騰華批評黃色經濟圈「對社會沒有好處」！","createTime":"2019-12-17T15:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T17:11:29.000Z","uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3a181c3335714345193e95e31ac1d76e93160d83","tid":1787034,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65cabeb268c284bfe15380f6fd7d0f61f92a631b","tid":1787034,"uid":64743,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:04:10.000Z","msg":"敵人反對我擁護<br />\n完"},{"pid":"4742ad03c1d8fa3ab437045dc4d3d8a19c1c9102","tid":1787034,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:04:11.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府舉辦新一輪「社區對話」，問責官員輪流在facebook回應網民留言。 <br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華是進行首場網上「社區對話」的官員，為時約五十分鐘，除了回應網民即時留言外，還收集連登、高登討論區等網站的發帖。<br />\n<br />\n政府表示不用公開對話的模式是考慮到上一次社區對話有發言的市民被「起底」。<br />\n<br />\n對於有支持反修例市民提出建立黃色經濟圈，邱騰華認為這樣做對社會沒有好處。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=373741&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D373741%26refer%3DShare&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2Bum5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=3d3b8e1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D373741%26refer%3DShare&h=342822f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=373741&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"929b8b3a431ef354f0a73d9d9dcb2373f81398b4","tid":1787034,"uid":200663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:05:15.000Z","msg":"敵人反對的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27caee542ffcdb9106cfe3ec1bbc2bfc57ad410","tid":1787034,"uid":291309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:05:33.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，對抗中資！<br />\n<br />\n中資係香港已成市場毒藥！